36. Business Logic
Profit Calculation

Automatically calculate:

Profit = Sales − Expenses

Users never enter profit manually.

Business Date

Automatically detect:

Local timezone
Current date
Day of week

Users never enter:

Date
Day
Missing Reports

If a report is missing for a business day:

Create a virtual record.

Display:

Sales

Nil

Expenses

Nil

Profit

Nil

Status

No Business Report Submitted

Never estimate missing values.

37. Outstanding Debt Logic

Outstanding Debt equals:

Sum of all debts

where

Status = Outstanding

Paid debts must never be included.

