Outstanding Debt

50,000
38. Business Score Logic (MVP)

Business Score ranges from:

0–100

Calculate using five equally weighted factors.

Factor	Weight
Profit Trend	20%
Sales Consistency	20%
Expense Control	20%
Debt Recovery	20%
Reporting Consistency	20%

Example:

Profit Trend

18

Sales Consistency

20

Expense Control

17

Debt Recovery

16

Reporting Consistency

20

Business Score

91

Display:

Business Score

91 / 100
39. AI Insight Engine (MVP)

For the MVP, generate insights using simple rules.

Example rules:

If profit increased:

Your profit increased compared to last week.

If expenses increased:

Your expenses are increasing. Monitor spending carefully.

If debt reduced:

Outstanding debt has reduced this week.

If reports are missed:

You missed one business report this week.

Only display one featured insight on the Dashboard.

40. Dashboard Refresh Logic

After saving today's business:

Immediately:

Calculate profit.
Save report.
Update Business Score.
Update Outstanding Debt.
Generate Insight.
Return to Dashboard.
Refresh KPI cards.

No page reload should be required.

41. Business History Logic

Business History displays:

Every business day in chronological order.

Submitted days:

Display values.

Missing days:

Display Nil.

Never remove missing days.

This ensures reports remain accurate.

